{"tid":875352,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英警起訴打人央視女記者","createTime":"2018-10-25T00:24:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T01:37:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"09c151b63037f89a179b6808e80209db609f98cf","tid":875352,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T00:24:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181025/20530400\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181025%2F20530400&d=WH4z3l63UHloRvjD8jbChzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=1f6604ae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181025%2F20530400&h=5fb808ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181025/20530400</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年10月25日 <br />\n<br />\n英警起訴打人央視女記者<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181025/large/25la9p19.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181025%2Flarge%2F25la9p19.jpg&h=cce28b44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n孔琳琳上月底在伯明翰大鬧由英國保守黨舉行的香港座談會。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上月底在伯明翰大鬧英國保守黨座談會的央視女記者孔琳琳，已被英國警方落案起訴普通襲擊，下月提訊。<br />\n<br />\n根據香港英文網媒Hong Kong Free Press報道，倫敦West Midlands 警方已落案起訴現年48歲、居於Kings Cross的孔琳琳，她將於下月七日在伯明翰裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n座談會上斥嘉賓「漢奸」<br />\n<br />\n孔琳琳上月底在伯明翰、由英國保守黨舉行的香港座談會大吵大鬧，斥在場嘉賓「分裂中國」、「漢奸」及「反中」等，被請離場期間更掌摑一名香港留學生義工工作人員，事後被英國伯明翰警方拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n事件引發中國外交部及中央電視台先後發動聲明抗議，要求英方道歉，演變成外交風波。<br />\n<br />\n事發時目擊女記者打人經過的香港眾志主席羅冠聰曾指，當時座談會已進入尾聲，正由保守黨人權委員會副主席Benedict Rogers作總結發言，期間Rogers提到自己是支持中國，並非反中，台下一名女士忽然「好大反應」大吵大鬧，「在場人士普遍都好厭惡佢呢種行為，係好無禮貌」。<br />\n<br />\n當日事發的場合，是英國保守黨人權委員會在保守黨年會會場舉行的「邊緣會議」（fringe meeting），戴耀廷、李柱銘、羅冠聰，以及香港監察（Hong Kong Watch）主席羅傑斯（Benedict Rogers）均應邀出席，主題是「香港自由、法治和自治的侵蝕」，由保守黨人權委員會主席布魯斯（Fiona Bruce）主持會議。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n花灑頭採防自殺設計<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n醫管局否決捐器官前驗戊肝"},{"pid":"99a844402675e7fcd7ac2a51b7e02fb74241d061","tid":875352,"uid":82532,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T00:30:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c283c089cba250ab1799ec94592a4ffd6d60369","tid":875352,"uid":1221,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T00:45:05.000Z","msg":"取消居英權 遣返中國 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2269c7fd303127eeae3fdfcd26b236ac68dc00f","tid":875352,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1c283c089cba250ab1799ec94592a4ffd6d60369","tid":875352,"uid":1221,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T00:45:05.000Z","msg":"取消居英權 遣返中國 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T00:57:09.000Z","msg":"呢樣先最驚"},{"pid":"6c94e4b34585acb345048e612aeb71df13f8d442","tid":875352,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T00:58:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9679167955186140109dfcc6b0e8b91954690e96","tid":875352,"uid":3177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T00:59:20.000Z","msg":"打返大陸抵撚死 咁撚愛國<br />\n<br />\n佢依啲黨媒都用左好多方法先留低做野<br />\n<br />\n抵！"},{"pid":"68d60729889f5d2c88df53e3d0111557c824a67d","tid":875352,"uid":2795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T01:29:19.000Z","msg":"出到外國先敢吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c678608ce898cd10116ec8845c40aa5b8499126","tid":875352,"u